messages.text: ugh why am I still at work??!!
bc you're almost done paying off student loans so you can focus full time on your comedy.
thanks, Dash. you know you’re the only person on Tinder that I’ve ever been this intimate with, right?
wow...and we haven’t even actually met IRL.
whose fault is that? ☺
let’s fix that.
meet me today on the reborn rails where 10 and 17 meet
what? lol
you keep saying your life lacks excitement so I made you an adventure
and at its end is your charming prince...Dashiell :)
ur joking, right?
I have a super important client today if I manage to get her company to sign with us the commission will be huge.
can’t you push it to tomorrow?
today is the only day I can meet because I have important business in Europe
seize the day, Rachel.
is dinner is included in this adventure?
of course.
oh god I did it! I sent an e-mail actually asking a client to reschedule
I’VE NEVER DONE THAT BEFORE...EVER!!
excellent.
now where am I going?
it’s all in the clue, “meet me today on reborn rails where 10 and 17 meet”
10 and 17? are those streets?
I can’t give you any hints!
but you’re doing well!
reborn rails…
HIGHLINE PARK…the repurposed NYC railway!
omg I’ve been meaning to visit that for ages.
aren’t you glad you called out sick? ☺
I’ll see you there. I’m taking the A train now!
I’m here!
this place is stunning.
its so lush. its like I’m almost able to forget I live in the most stressful city in the world
I’m glad you like it
where are you?
I’m like the only single person here. this is exactly why I never go to places like this
I’m not there.
what do you mean you’re not there?
you haven’t found it yet?
lol
nice touch with the velvet envelope
a parking pass?
you can drive, right?
I’ve never driven in the city!
don’t worry, you won’t be in the city for long.
you planned this well. the parking garage was like two steps away from the highline.
crap. that client just e-mailed me back. she says we need to meet this afternoon.
OMG.
this is your car?
don’t hurt my baby.
I’ve never ridden in a sports car before!!!
not just any sports car: a black corvette convertible.
I can’t blow off this client. if I don’t meet her this afternoon, it’ll jeopardize the deal.
it’s up to you, but your destination is in the GPS.
it’s a 5 hour trip!
you’ll be riding up one of the most beautiful highways in America seeing Vermont fall colors.
can’t believe I’m doing this…but this is just too amazing.
so you’re coming?
yes, but I’m coming back tomorrow!
of course. ☺
you made me a playlist?
hilarious first choice song btw
Brave by Sara Bareillis
I thought so, too :)
let me know when you’re close
I need to get everything ready for tonight
will do. I can’t wait to finally see you in person!
me too
a few hours later
wow this is so beautiful. you can’t see this type of foliage in nyc
the trees, the mountains, the cute little houses
I’m still about two hours away ☹
I can’t wait till I can finally place my lips on yours
just a little longer, love.
it’s gotten dark, really quick.
they haven’t heard of street lights in Vermont?
I think I’m here??
a near empty parking lot in the middle of nowhere?
I’m in the car. The gps, can’t locate the house so I figured I’d meet you and you can follow me
that bucket of bolts in the corner?
I only have one corvette ;)
okay. Why are you staying in the car?
it’s not the right time for us to meet
just follow me up to the yurt
yurt?
it’s like a tent.
a tent...I don’t like the sound of that
ok. this doesn’t look so bad I guess. it’s like a little house.
describe it like that next time.
go inside. I’ll meet you in there.
I need to prepare some other stuff.
you know me too well :D
bbq lovers pizza, champaign, and Jane the Virgin.
where are you? we should be sharing this together.
I haven’t been fully honest with you
you didn’t catfish me, right?
um…
omg no
my name’s not Dashiell
I’m not a rich European bonds trader
I made the Dashiell account as a joke, but then I met you.
can I come inside and properly introduce myself.
NO!
you don’t do this to someone.
I lost a major client.
I’m going have to work a whole another year now.
I thought you rescheduled??
you don’t reschedule in my industry. I lost it for someone who doesn’t even exist!
I’m sorry. I didn’t know. I just - it had to be today. the corvette and yurt are rentals.
I want to go home.
you don’t even want to hear what I have to say?
no. I’ve never been so embarrassed in my life.
ok, you’re right. this was stupid. I’m sorry.
I’m in my car. you can follow me in the corvette.
the corvette is fired up, let’s go.
I just want you to know I’m so sorry.
stop talking.
I know you don’t want me to talk, but I need to say this or else I’ll regret it.
I didn’t mean to trick you. I made the account as a joke.
I was so lonely and I wasn’t getting any hits on Tinder.
It was so easy...I just threw up a fake picture of a beautiful man and I never received so much attention in my life, but I didn’t really hit it off with anyone.
then I met you. and it’s like we just clicked, I didn’t need to try so hard
and I just thought...well, that all of this might show you how much I actually cared
just drive. you don’t lie to someone like this.
I won’t say anything else.
had you not lied to me, this would actually have been amazing.
thanks
ten minutes later
just out of curiosity…if I had stayed… did you have desert planned?
red velvet and vanilla cupcakes from Magnolia Bakery
omg. YUM. do you have them in the car?
no they’re at the yurt.
we need to go back
so you’ll give me a chance?
let’s just take it one cupcake at a time. ;)
